column5: I'm thinking about hitting up Rice on my day off tomorrow. How are the bass biting? How thick are the weeds?
Was there Saturday was a zoo, the weeds are getting thick, managed a few nice fish, but people every where.
Ya, I bet eh. Rice is always packed, it seems.  Did you get Largemouth or Smallmouth?
We've been putting a hurtin on the eyes there all season this year.  I might head out there too.......I"m off wed/thurs.  S.
